Mine was the old {{champion:43}} 
I absolutely loved her Q and E - she had nice damage and was difficult to kill and worked so well with slippery ADCs such as {{champion:81}}
However, with all the cc now in the game, I doubt she would've worked. Shame.

Recently, {{champion:7}} had her w made (figuratively) useless. Her instant burst and run removed, forcing her to wait for 1.5 sec.

Now I only have {{champion:117}} {{champion:99}} {{champion:103}} left.
